      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这个表的主键用什么类型？还有，客户信息是外键关联对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id",
        "customer_id",
        "FK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，主键用bigint的自增ID。customer_id关联客户表，也是bigint。另外需要记录配送方式，比如快递、自提这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id",
